item.title: kimchiest.com
item.description: Ok I did it again, I couldn’t stand with notion anymore even though it’s simple and easy to maintain. I want to make my blog fast no javescript, minimum lines of code fully functional still Now kimchiest.com is 10 mb big and 9.6 mb are from media (picture) so it’s pretty good :D It still has darkmode but only works when your device is set to darkmode.

item.title: chelseastayshealthy.com
